Pete Buttigieg Talks Being Gay in Conservative StatesPete Buttigieg talks on The Advocate's podcast, LGBTQ&A, about how he'll navigate his queerness in more conservative states.
Few queer politicians have garnered as much attention as Pete Buttigieg, let alone a queer politician running for the highest office in the land.
Now, as he begins to campaign throughout the country, Buttigieg will have to figure out what exactly that's going to look like.
Preparing to sit down with Pete Buttigieg for my podcast, LGBTQ&A, code-switching was at the front of my mind.
Upcoming guests include Pete Buttigieg, Roxane Gay, Amiyah Scott, and Ryan O'Connell.